         <div type="notes">
            <note xml:id="n04051701" n="1">Perhaps applications to join the expedition.</note>
            <note xml:id="n04051702" n="2">Probably a mistake; the court-martial record below says that <name type="person" key="Hall, Hugh">Hall</name> and <name type="person" key="Werner, William">Werner</name> were to be granted leniency and only <name type="person" key="Collins, John">Collins</name> was to be punished. None of the enlisted men's journals mention the affair.</note>
            <note xml:id="n04051703" n="3">The order and court-martial record in the Orderly Book, including the signatures, are in <name type="person" key="Ordway, John">Ordway's</name> hand.</note>
